Classes
Class
Description
Course
The Course class represents a course in a university.
courseController
The courseController class is responsible for controlling the client-side operations related to Course management.
CourseView
This class represents the UI for the course list view, which displays a table of courses and allows the user to filter by season.
Main
The Main class is responsible for launching the client application.
registrationController
The registrationController class is responsible for handling the communication between the client and the server for registration-related functionality.
RegistrationForm
The RegistrationForm class represents a registration form for a course.
RegistrationView
This class represents the view for registering to a course.
